# Purpose:								#
# To ask the daemon to re-open it's log file which is necessary after	#
# rotating the logs. Also request the daemon to write summary stats to	#
# the syslog.								#
#									#
# Syntax:	dnsmasq-postrotate.sh [ -h --help || -V --version ]	#
#									#
# Exit Codes:	0 - success						#
#		1 - failure						#
